config APP_LEGOPORT
	tristate "LEGO Powered Up I/O port utility"
	default n
	---help---
		CLI for inspecting and waiting on /dev/legoport0..5
		(Issue #42).  Subcommands: list, info, wait, stats.

		With CONFIG_LEGO_LUMP_DIAG=y, also exposes the
		`lump-hw dump` subcommand that triggers a kernel-side
		register dump for the 6 LUMP UARTs (Issue #43 Phase 1).
